sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Bench as Benchmark Runner
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker
    participant Svc as Any Service (e.g. ASR)

    Note over Bench: Start Latency Test (N=100)

    %% Injection
    Bench->>Kafka: Inject Event (T0 timestamp inside payload)
    
    %% Parallel Observation
    par Service Processing
        Kafka->>Svc: Consume Event
        Svc->>Svc: Process (Compute)
        Svc->>Kafka: Produce Output Event
    and Measurement Observation
        Kafka-->>Bench: Consumer: Input Topic (Log T0)
        Kafka-->>Bench: Consumer: Output Topic (Log T1)
    end

    Note over Bench: Latency = T1 - T0
    Bench->>Bench: Store Metric in Report